!! GNU General Public License, see ~abinit/COPYING
!! or http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.txt .
!! For the initials of contributors, see ~abinit/doc/developers/contributors.txt .
!!
!! CHILDREN
!! interfaces_77_suscep.F90
!! m_suscep_stat.F90
!!
!!***
